{"tid":2130013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"戴耀廷： 會向港大校監林鄭月娥提出上訴","createTime":"2020-07-29T03:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T04:58:28.000Z","uid":22556,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a91b6d2f79fb1d851d1a3004835ca19562c62aba","tid":2130013,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T03:56:21.000Z","msg":"因保密原則，我不能公開大學的文件，但與律師團隊商量後，我向大學提交的文件是可以公開的。公眾可從我提交的文件中，大概掌握爭議的地方是甚麼：<br />\n<br />\n戴耀廷向香港大學教務委員會提交的陳詞: <a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/mtxeh6wr0suuvvx/200427%20Ltr%20to%20Senate%28with%20encl%29.pdf?dl=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dropbox.com%2Fs%2Fmtxeh6wr0suuvvx%2F200427%2520Ltr%2520to%2520Senate%2528with%2520encl%2529.pdf%3Fdl%3D0&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6dVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=a31309ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dropbox.com/s/mtxeh6wr0suuvvx/200427%20Ltr%20to%20Senate%28with%20encl%29.pdf?dl=0</a><br />\n<br />\n相關附件: <a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/nfxyupq2uo9vkwf/200504%20Ltr%20to%20Senate%28with%20encl%29.pdf?dl=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dropbox.com%2Fs%2Fnfxyupq2uo9vkwf%2F200504%2520Ltr%2520to%2520Senate%2528with%2520encl%2529.pdf%3Fdl%3D0&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6dVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=09a6d84f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dropbox.com/s/nfxyupq2uo9vkwf/200504%20Ltr%20to%20Senate%28with%20encl%29.pdf?dl=0</a><br />\n<br />\n戴耀廷向香港大學校務委員會提交的陳詞: <a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/x7g0lsrl4dhgm4d/200723%20Submissions%20to%20Council.pdf?dl=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dropbox.com%2Fs%2Fx7g0lsrl4dhgm4d%2F200723%2520Submissions%2520to%2520Council.pdf%3Fdl%3D0&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6dVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=52d7be35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dropbox.com/s/x7g0lsrl4dhgm4d/200723%20Submissions%20to%20Council.pdf?dl=0</a><br />\n<br />\n我決定向香港大學校監，即特首林鄭月娥，就校委會辭退我的決定提出上訴。<br />\n雖然我知道這上訴不可能成功，但我不會讓林鄭月娥在傷害香港學術自由的事上，可以置身事外。大學以外勢力推翻大學的決定，是昭然若揭。<br />\n之後是否會提出司法覆核，仍有待與律師團隊商量。<br />\n<br />\n雖然離開了港大的崗位，但法治的研究及教學工作，我是不會停下來的。<br />\n我計劃用一至兩年時間完成一本有關法治的普及讀物。<br />\n我亦會在香港社區推動法治教育。<br />\n當然，我會為香港法治的重生而繼續抗爭。<br />\n我希望也能支援其他為香港法治重生而戰的人。<br />\n要開展這些工作，我需要您的支持。<br />\n只要能堅持下去，我們必會見到香港法治重生的一天。<br />\n很希望您能成為我的 patron，請點擊以下連結：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://patreon.com/bennytai\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpatreon.com%2Fbennytai&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6dVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=4282726c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://patreon.com/bennytai</a><br />\n<br />\n就讓我們一起為香港法治的重生努力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/270507093143059/posts/1455745527952537/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F270507093143059%2Fposts%2F1455745527952537%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6dVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=3a9208d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/270507093143059/posts/1455745527952537/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"646f57ef96d86b37c8a64224c9f53cb8a912e1ea","tid":2130013,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T04:03:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLHXJen.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLHXJen.gif&h=6f0d3a7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00ffa9ad21bcba95c703f35a55791bb7d9227a2a","tid":2130013,"uid":72457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T04:07:58.000Z","msg":"英國人話唔關林鄭事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"443773fff163b4ccbd0a944810054b38de505034","tid":2130013,"uid":324984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T04:58:28.000Z","msg":"一定支持 ！"}]}